{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/swiftui_DropBox/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"swiftui-list\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#swiftui-list\" aria-label=\"swiftui list permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SwiftUI List</h3>\n<p>SwiftUI에서 기본으로 제공해주는 DisclosureGroup이 있지만 커스텀에 제약이 많다...\n직접 DropDown을 만들어 여러 속성을 추가해서 커스텀할 수 있도록 짠 코드이다.</p>\n<p>expand변수를 통해서 box를 열었을 때, 닫았을 때를 체크해줬다.</p>\n<p>그리고 <code class=\"language-text\">.animation(.spring())</code>로 애니메이션도 추가할 수 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"dropdown-struct\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dropdown-struct\" aria-label=\"dropdown struct permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DropDown struct</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">DropDown</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">View</span><spa